{"id":"mushi","term":"Mushi","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Receding, the second of the two sons of Merari (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Exodus 6:19\">Ex. 6:19</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Numbers 3:20\">Num. 3:20</a>). His sons were called Mushites (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Numbers 3:33\">Num. 3:33</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Numbers 26:58\">26:58</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Exodus 6:19","Numbers 3:20","Numbers 3:33","Numbers 26:58"]}